               <physDesc>
                  <p>3 papyri ; fr. 1: 10.3 x 10.3 cm; fr. ii: 2.9 x 3.4 cm; fr. 3 0.5 x 0.5 cm</p>
                  <objectDesc>
                     <p>
                        <note type="conservation">The papyrus is broken off at the left and the bottom sides. There is a manufacturer kollesis at the right hand side c. 2,5 cm. The ink of the recto side as the papyrus was folded left some traces on the verso. Actually the back of the two right folded parts were on top of the recto of the other two left folded parts.</note>
                     </p>
